{"tid":1753980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最新風向：大家已經贏咗，俾啲掌聲自己!","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:28:52.000Z","uid":336896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7a08a7747fde0c0527428540b20f18cfdba13b","tid":1753980,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"呢篇係分化 post，不喜勿入。<br />\n鬧緊你地呀！<br />\n<br />\n又話全港幾百萬人支持，<br />\n又話區選顯示民意，<br />\n但係平時叫大家大三罷，有幾多人嚮應?<br />\n個個都話要返工，不了。<br />\n宜家最大問題唔係黃絲唔夠多，<br />\n而係冷氣黃絲太多呀！<br />\n成日以為淨係放工出黎行吓，<br />\npart-time 抗爭，<br />\nFB share 吓，連登吹吓水，<br />\n以為咁就可以推翻個政權?<br />\n冇勇武流咗咁多血，你地會贏倒區選咩?<br />\n黎明行動停止，<br />\n裝修停止，<br />\n連儂牆停止，<br />\n前線手足係咪已成 condom?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">繼續行動，直至有真普選為止!</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a1c16918984607c89b0b6901bab817b831e22ff","tid":1753980,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bd49b684619ffac806b53cd1488983c7a680e65b","tid":1753980,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"革命尚未成功 手足仍需努力"},{"pid":"5700bd39cf85af452836ab3656a7a9d